        <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Visa Document Information</h1>
        <p class="govuk-body">Please ensure you have all the required documents ready for your visa application.</p>
        <ul class="govuk-list">
          <li>
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-s">Visa Application Form</h2>
            <div>
              <p class="govuk-body">Completed and signed application form provided by the consulate or embassy.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-s">Photograph ID</h2>
            <div>
              <p class="govuk-body">Recent passport-sized photo (white background, no glasses, head uncovered).</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-s">Passport</h2>
            <div>
              <p class="govuk-body">Original passport with at least 6 months validity and two blank pages.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-s">Nombramiento</h2>
            <div>
              <p class="govuk-body">Official job offer or appointment letter, signed by the Spanish educational institution.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-s">Health Insurance</h2>
            <div>
              <p class="govuk-body">Private health insurance covering full duration of stay in Spain with no copayments.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-s">Criminal Record</h2>
            <div>
              <p class="govuk-body">Background check issued within the last 3 months, legalized and apostilled if required.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-s">Medical Certificate</h2>
            <div>
              <p class="govuk-body">Doctorâ€™s note confirming you do not suffer from any diseases that may have public health repercussions.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-s">Visa Application Payment</h2>
            <div>
              <p class="govuk-body">Proof of payment or exact fee in cash/card, depending on your consulate's instructions.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
